node.text: Hey everybody - welcome to my new IGTV series, "Real Ariel". I wanted to get on here and talk about music, my likes and dislikes, who I am, and what I'm up to. I'm making this up as I go, so please send feedback -- what do you wanna know about, what else should I share? thanks for checking it out and keep following me every week on IGTV
